<custom_item>
  type        : CONFIG_CHECK
  description : "JUNI-RT-000800 - The Juniper multicast edge router must be configured to establish boundaries for administratively scoped multicast traffic."
  info        : "If multicast traffic is forwarded beyond the intended boundary, it is possible that it can be intercepted by unauthorized or unintended personnel.

